The paper deals with image security and cryptography, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of framelet transform and cellular automata suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also involves image processing and analysis, which could place it under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the use of chaos maps and security analysis suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY).
